    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives but has some mechanical wear that may require attention in the near term. The exterior shows noticeable scratches and minor dents, and the interior has visible wear including some staining and worn surfaces. It is a usable vehicle but buyers should expect to put some work into it.",
